text = "[b][color=#6bb8ff]Exclude Folders from Search[/color][/b]

Right-click on any folder and select \"Exclude from Search\" to skip it during deep searches. This can drastically improve search performance for large directories like node_modules, .git, or build folders.

---

[b][color=#6bb8ff]Quick Navigation with Favorites[/color][/b]

Press the star icon to add the current folder to your favorites. Use number keys 1-9 to quickly jump to favorites. Key 1 always navigates to your project folder.

---

[b][color=#6bb8ff]Regex Search[/color][/b]

Click the \".*\" button to enable regex search. Use patterns like \"player.*\\.png\" to find files matching complex naming patterns.

---

[b][color=#6bb8ff]Filter by Type[/color][/b]

Use the Filter dropdown to quickly show only specific file types (Images, Sounds, Videos, etc.). Combined with Deep search, this lets you find all assets of a type across your entire folder structure.

---

[b][color=#6bb8ff]Flat List Mode[/color][/b]

Toggle the tree/list button to switch between tree view and flat list mode. Flat list shows all files in the current folder and subfolders as a single scrollable list - great for browsing large asset collections."
